QUESTION NO: 1
A customer is interested in purchasing the following modules:
Accounts Payable
Accounts Receivable
General Ledger
Project Controller

B. Business Essentials
C. Multi-User Standard
D. Professional

QUESTION NO: 7
Which of the following statements describe Microsoft Dynamics SL referential integrity? Choose
the 2 that apply.
